TSP_GA - Class in GA
This class encodes all the logic and design of the Genetic Algorithm that was applied for TSP symmetric instances
TSP_GA() - Constructor for class GA.TSP_GA
The TSP_GA() Constructor is the default constructor with default parameters set , which are the most effective parameters as suggested by papers and as noted by experiment.

This constructor is used to set up the parameters as desired by the user
